data.description:
Welcome to this charming cabin in Conifer!  Fall in love with the vaulted ceilings and skylights in this one bedroom / one bath mountain home.  So many improvements inside and out have been completed to make this home move in ready.  All you need are your personal belongings and you!  Besides the updates featured in the kitchen, bathroom, flooring, and lighting, there are many behind the scenes upgrades that add value to the home.  Newer foundation with Helical Piers, newer roof and gutters, tankless water heater, newer electrical wiring throughout, newer plumbing, newer HVAC.  Upstairs loft can act as an office or flex space or even one’s bedroom area (without a closet).  Larger mud room with washer & dryer included.  
An additional smaller wood cabin is included with the property that has a breaker and outlets (but currently not hooked up).
Conveniently located to Highway 285, grocery stores, shops, and eateries.

Please note this property consists of 3 lots, 10812 Fox Trot Lane, 10802 Fox Trot Lane, and 10792 Fox Trot Lane.  The lot square footage listed is the combination of all 3 lots.  The legal descriptions for 10802 and 10792 are not included in this MLS, but will be provided by the title company.  Buyer to verify info regarding square footage, lot size, schools, taxes, etc.
